    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2012-04-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2012-06-06T15:53:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Small Business Tax Simplification Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt certain small business taxpayers from the requirements of using the accrual method of accounting and of using inventories. Allows such taxpayers to use a cash method of accounting if they meet the gross receipts test and are not engaged in farming as a corporation. Increases the amount of the gross receipts test to $10 million (currently, $5 million) and permits an annual inflation adjustment of that amount. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
